+	/*   AT
+	 *  TFR   EV X F   IHD LR    S
+	 * .EEE ..EE PUI. .TAT 4RVI ZWRS BLDP WCAM
+	 * rxxx rrxx xxx0 0101 xxxx xxxx x111 xxxx < forced
+	 *   11    0 110    1  0011 1100 .111 1101 < we want
